# Agentic morloc code exploration

This purpose of this repo is to organize an agentic exploration of morloc
program space.

The ../src/content folder contains the morloc documentation. Any deviation
between the docs and the morloc operation should be considered a bug worth
reporting, as should any features of morloc that are not reported in docs.

All agents will work in their vagrant VMs using the latest morloc version that
can be downloaded with `morloc-manager install`.


  Coding-Agents Pipeline

            ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │            SHARED INPUTS               │
